high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the couch.
Pick up the remote that is above the blue credit card on the couch.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the tall lamp in the corner of the room.
Turn on the light of the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote in the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn left to face the sofa.
Pick up the back remote control closest to the back of the sofa.
Turn left and move to stand in front of the lamp in the corner.
Turn on the lamp to look at the remote control in the light.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control by the light of the lamp.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the couch.
Pick the remote that is further back up from the couch.
Go to the left and face the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a remote and turn a lamp on.
